ConstraintSolver
public static enum ConstraintSolver.OPTIONS
extends java.lang.Enum<ConstraintSolver.OPTIONS>

General class options. Options currently available:

  • AUTO_PROPAGATE: if set, the constraint solver will call (user implemented) propagate method automatically. Do not set if propagations must be dealt with in a more sophisticated way (e.g., incremental propagators). Default is false.
  • DOMAINS_AUTO_INSTANTIATED: if set, the constraint solver will not check whether domains are instantiated before propagation. Default is false.
